Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.78,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs23\pos(593,182)\c&HCBAF98&\3c&HFFFFFF&}一\N\N般\N\N对\N\N局\N\N室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.78,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs23\pos(563,188)\c&HCBAF98&\3c&HFFFFFF&}中\N\N\N级\N\N\N课\N\N\N程
